  "text": "In a previous study, we investigated the PEC synthesis of p-anisaldehyde from 4-metoxybenzyl alcohol in water, under UV irradiation [CITATION_1] by using Ti/TiO 2 photoanodes prepared both by thermal oxidation and dip-coating methods. The photoanodes prepared by thermal oxidation showed better aldehyde selectivity and activity performance than dip-coated ones.",
